---
title: Skillet Chicken with Balsamic Plums and Thyme Roasted Potatoes
description: In this weeknight winner, we've coated juicy plums in balsamic and drizzled them with a chicken pan jus! Thyme-roasted potatoes and fresh-picked basil bring this dish together for a refined take on chicken thighs!
